<br>
Since you fail to give any reason behind your comment, I will have to assume that you did not read the first part of my post, so I guess I will spell it out for you.<br>
<br>
SoS -- normal cast time 8 sec<br>
Spell Haste 4 (i.e. mage ring): -15% cast time =&gt; SoS cast time of 6.8 sec.<br>
<br>
Blessing of Reverence: -10% cast time (stacks with Spell Haste 4) =&gt; SoS cast time of 6 seconds.<br>
<br>
Draught -- normal cast time 3 sec<br>
Cast time with Spell Haste: 2.55 secs<br>
Cast time with BoR (on top of Spell Haste): 2.25 secs<br>
<br>
T-staff will not affect the same spell after the patch a month or two ago, but it WILL refresh spell icons, and allow you to cast a DIFFERENT spell.<br>
<br>
